Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.54,0:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹竿喔，要買竹竿嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.21,0:01:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹竿喔，要買竹竿嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.29,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不要的東西嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過這裡的夏天很熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會這麼熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季才剛過\N熱成這樣太不正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想裝台冷氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點中暑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中暑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指天氣太熱而沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.43,0:02:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.53,0:02:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能老是這麼懶散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正補習班也有冷氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.04,0:02:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點去讀書好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#14  小ちぃ，招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全館空調系統檢測通知）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在下一節課前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷氣就會修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.97,0:03:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.15,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在出個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人答得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.62,0:03:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會我請大家吃刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.39,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要草莓牛奶冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要答得出來才有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答題的學生要由我來選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.07,0:03:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來回答看看\N課本第25頁的第3題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最基礎的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉例說明好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常用到的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼熱啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為冷氣壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄壞的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干我什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看起來很鬱卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你今天有沒有空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在打工前有點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一節英文課的筆記\N能不能借我抄一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.91,0:04:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請你吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的字也未免太潦草了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.19,0:05:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個像顛倒音符的是什麼字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是U啦，U
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也叫U啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正內容是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.71,0:05:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將英語課本\N第158頁第六行開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯成英文吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether         we         shouId         pIaced
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among         the         causes\Nof         happiness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or         among         the         causes\Nof         unhappiness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.09,0:05:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may         perhaps         be         regarded\Nas         a         dreadfuI         question
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯\NThere         is         certainIy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了，絲茉茉\NThere         is         certainIy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你這裡抄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉頭腦真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉裝有英日翻譯軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也做得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能幫你出題目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻方便的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想借絲茉茉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是報答你借我筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借你一天沒關係喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠電腦好像不太對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該去打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筆記晚點再還我就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜，謝謝請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師在上課時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有提到\N明天可能會有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐給的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我放在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得聞到這個味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓人有夏天的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫作夏天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣熱是夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.84,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣冷是冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣溫暖是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚會是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，竟然把人家給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.59,0:07:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是忘了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.09,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是夏天的錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.79,0:08:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一場夏日的回憶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有玩弄妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的，認真的，誠心的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是本須和的房間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有男生房間的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼自己跑進來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎，別在意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.03,0:08:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀\Nちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妳叫小ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是孺子可教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝給他醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳才剛喝過不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好不容易…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說要住一晚是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼行不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼做比較好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法熬到天亮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣更不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是願意讓我住一晚囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事我可不管喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我做什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.18,0:09:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳打算喝這麼多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，很平常，很平常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹教過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.97,0:09:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個形狀怎麼形容？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在笑的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是好想當喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.95,0:10:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.38,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳原本想當小學老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，原本是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我老公說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小學要是當了班導師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會忙到沒時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被老公反對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.34,0:10:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.58,0:10:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請妳下來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.06,0:11:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.79,0:11:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該停了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“國王遊戲”很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你籤運那麼差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就繼續玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像個男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽籤的時候乾脆點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，小ちぃ也抽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.65,0:11:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，做什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該做點刺激的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺激？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到二號的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請拿到二號的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手舉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是幾號？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又好像有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.08,0:12:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩親親囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.12,0:12:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眼神已經不正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要親囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.43,0:12:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.87,0:12:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是本須和的電腦嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要嚇我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有精神起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有想歪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是想其他的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.92,0:13:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砰一聲倒下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我睡著了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吵醒小ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經天亮了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只穿內衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在夢裡一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…\N早安，小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，臉濕透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，妳那個穿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.14,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒欺負你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺負…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟第一次要給喜歡的人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和你還是很純潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是天氣熱脫下衣服而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟本須和都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.03,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算一般尺寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般尺寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹是一般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ，這個不必記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我盥洗一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.94,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有牙刷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一開始就打算來借住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就打算在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…為什麼妳要來這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為膽小吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.67,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.79,0:16:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這位上禮拜在海邊見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，敝姓清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，補習班的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.88,0:17:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天功課一定進步不少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直嘆氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被她誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在在意那個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下次去幫你解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這確實讓人傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被誤會跟我在交往的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.15,0:17:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是老師比較傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.95,0:17:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師在煩惱些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以說給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以找我談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟我聽到的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個在室男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個跟現在說的無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.07,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天清水老師突然來我房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.99,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始點名…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.14,0:19:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.84,0:19:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，點名就不用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，翻開第26頁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是慘斃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保一副可怕的表情\N一句話也不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我為他操心\N打工時老出錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要被雨淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早點睡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.51,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口為什麼濕了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.81,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子真是一點也不老實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不老實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上的妝都糊掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的女人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子最可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會被人看見喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.96,0:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.01,0:22:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.12,0:22:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.33,0:22:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.37,0:23:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.29,0:23:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.43,0:23:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.47,0:23:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.15,0:23:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班教書的是老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.70,0:23:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班讀書的是學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是補習班老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師\N跟補習班學生抱在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個補習班學生是新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是有夫之婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.11,0:23:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.85,0:23:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.81,0:24:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.08,0:24:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「小ちぃ，什麼都不做」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.89,0:24:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也只能這樣
